<item>
            <title>[SLING-1135] ClassLoaderFacade must overwrite ClassLoader.loadClass(String, boolean)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SLING-1135</link>
                <project id="12310710" key="SLING">Sling</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currenly the ClassLoaderFacade overwrites the ClassLoader.loadClass(String) method. This prevents this class (returned as the result of the DynamicClassLoaderManager.getDynamicClassLoader()) from being used as the parent to other class loaders.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The reason is, that class loaders call their parent class loader&apos;s loadClass(String, boolean) method to check for the class in the parent class loader.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
